#: filewidgets/kfilewidget.cpp:1216
#, kde-format
msgid ""
"<qt>Click this button to enter the parent folder.<br /><br />For instance, "
"if the current location is file:/home/konqi clicking this button will take "
"you to file:/home.</qt>"
msgstr ""
"<qt>ወደ ወላጅ አቃፊው ለመግባት ይህንን አዝራር ጠቅ ያድርጉ።<br /><br />ለምሳሌ፣ የአሁኑ ቦታ ፋይል፦/home/"
"konqi ከሆነ ይህንን አዝራር ጠቅ ማድረግ ወደ ፋይል፦/home ይወስድዎታል።</qt>"

#: filewidgets/kfilewidget.cpp:1220
#, kde-format
