msgstr "የፋይል አይነት(&F)፦"

#: filewidgets/kfilewidget.cpp:2968
#, kde-format
msgid ""
"<qt>This is the file type selector. It is used to select the format that the "
"file will be saved as.</qt>"
msgstr "<qt>ይህ የፋይል አይነት መምረጫ ነው። ፋይሉ የሚቀመጥበትን ቅርጸት ለመምረጥ ይጠቀማል።</qt>"

#: filewidgets/kfilewidget.cpp:2970
